`UITheme` with specific color values (`0x1a1a1a`, etc.)\n- Animation using Phase
r tweens (`Back.out`, `Power2`)\n- Texture fallback using `hasTexture()`, `creat
eInkBackground()`\n- No React, Tailwind, or DOM concepts\n\nThe design spec in `
designs/issue-18/design-spec.md` contradicts the PRD entirely.\n\n### 3. No Code
