ng to PRD-004 Phase 1, the infrastructure should create:\n- `src/ui/types.ts` pu
blic types\n- Rewrite `src/ui/utils.ts`\n- `src/ui/__tests__/setup.ts`\n- `src/u
i/index.ts` unified exports\n\nNone of these actual code changes are present in 
